flowchart LR
  RecordButton[Record Button] -->|digital input| UNO[Arduino UNO Q]
  ConsentSwitch[Consent Switch] -->|digital input| UNO
  MarkButton[Mark Button] -->|digital input| UNO
  Power[Power: USB-C / regulated battery] --> UNO

  UNO -->|digital output| StatusLED[Status LED]
  UNO -->|PWM output| Buzzer[Buzzer]
  UNO -->|transistor-controlled output| Vibration[Vibration Motor]
  UNO <-->|I2C or SPI| Display[OLED / e-paper Display]

  Nicla[Nicla Vision: camera / audio / onboard IMU] <-->|Wi-Fi / BLE / serial bridge| UNO
  GNSS[Multi-constellation GNSS receiver] -->|UART| UNO
  RTC[RTC module] -->|I2C| UNO
  Magnetometer[Magnetometer] -->|I2C| UNO
  Pressure[Pressure sensor] -->|I2C| UNO
